Akira (J) [hM04][t1].nes<br />PRG ROM:    8 x 16KiB<br />CHR ROM:   32 x  8KiB<br />ROM CRC32:  0xdcb096a9<br />ROM MD5:  0x8a04b2495442ed9a63d43c870e7cf145<br />Mapper #:  4<br />Mapper name: MMC3<br />Mirroring: Horizontal<br />Battery-backed: No<br />Trained: Yes<br /><br />Only FCEUX can run it. I don't know if it has any bug.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4330">FARID</a> — Sat Dec 24, 2011 1:13 am</p><hr />
